  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support the Territorialization of the Public Policy of Attention, Assistance and Comprehensive Reparation to the Victims of the Internal Armed Conflict, in the Framework of the NDP 2018-2022. Phase III</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Through this project, IOM contributes to the creation of mechanisms that link stabilization planning instruments and capacity-building in the area of public policy with regards to victims in Colombia. This is done by developing the institutional capacities of the departments and municipalities to comply with their legal responsibilities, as well as providing technical assistance in follow-up tools and planning instruments to enable effective implementation of the victim-centered policies.</narrative>
  </description>
